{"tid":2457213,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"鄭月娥：今日針後能覺良好！","createTime":"2021-03-22T12:42:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T13:46:04.000Z","uid":230530,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f1e0e386bf3d8ce7f845c7a2e87794c67de4e733","tid":2457213,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:42:38.000Z","msg":"相隔了28日，今天我打了第二針科興疫苗，完成發揮疫苗的保護作用；過一段時間，我也會安排檢測體內的抗體，確定已產生一定的免疫力。<br />\n<br />\n過了整天，我没有任何不舒服，下午可以如常工作；不過專家早前提醒，第二針引起的反應可能會比第一針強，各位接種第二劑疫苗的市民應留意接種後身體情況。<br />\n<br />\n今日的確診個案維持在單位數，源頭未明的只有兩宗；政府則繼續就有確診個案的住宅大廈或工作地點發出強制檢測令，和進行相關的執法行動，實行多管齊下，防控疫情。<br />\n<br />\n請大家不要再猶豫了，護己護人，盡快接種新冠疫苗吧！<br />\n<br />\n#同心抗疫 #齊打疫苗 #林鄭月娥 #CarrieLam"},{"pid":"ba7dedc31a2030090c64cf1a03cdf95522f8331b","tid":2457213,"uid":327169,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:46:02.000Z","msg":"生產倒數開始 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e03d01c3b5d1e79d1ebde89b46ae2134eaefe57","tid":2457213,"uid":49004,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ba7dedc31a2030090c64cf1a03cdf95522f8331b","tid":2457213,"uid":327169,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:46:02.000Z","msg":"生產倒數開始 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:46:57.000Z","msg":"生命倒數開始"},{"pid":"abb0d1039f7170956ff8286af1f8f7129e7b5017","tid":2457213,"uid":327169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ba7dedc31a2030090c64cf1a03cdf95522f8331b","tid":2457213,"uid":327169,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:46:02.000Z","msg":"生產倒數開始 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /